This paper is primarily focused on the topic of malware detection and evasion, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also heavily utilizes machine learning techniques, specifically reinforcement learning, which suggests that it could also be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential impact on anti-malware vendors and their software, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SI).
